{"tid":2447130,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"截至去年底，社署已登記露宿者約有1,500人，是回歸以來有紀錄最多，但未計及沒登記人數","createTime":"2021-03-15T03:50:23.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-15T07:23:54.000Z","uid":36494,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"5b62f6fbac6fa14763e99289b58d12790178dd6d","tid":2447130,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T03:50:23.000Z","msg":"一個社會進步還是倒退，走到街頭一看或有答案。截至去年底，社署已登記露宿者約有1,500人，是回歸以來有紀錄最多，但未計及沒登記人數，而且在武漢肺炎疫情下，逾25萬人失業。社區組織協會估計，目前全港無家者超過2,000人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210315/CFRL4VDZKNAFDD24DKVV3HC5YQ/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR0_-WoKSK1ZT7xHOBPvKu2nc91K808s0_nKTO_cUMSY-hK3KM4bqJRcwlc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210315%2FCFRL4VDZKNAFDD24DKVV3HC5YQ%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR0_-WoKSK1ZT7xHOBPvKu2nc91K808s0_nKTO_cUMSY-hK3KM4bqJRcwlc&d=qonCz35ufBxMHQAS3tFcDnlPKE5%2BvOhv5kPCmhOEeDs%3D&h=f83f5aae\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210315%2FCFRL4VDZKNAFDD24DKVV3HC5YQ%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR0_-WoKSK1ZT7xHOBPvKu2nc91K808s0_nKTO_cUMSY-hK3KM4bqJRcwlc&h=251f495e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210315/CFRL4VDZKNAFDD24DKVV3HC5YQ/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR0_-WoKSK1ZT7xHOBPvKu2nc91K808s0_nKTO_cUMSY-hK3KM4bqJRcwlc</a><br />\n<br />\n「你見到出面住嘅人係越來越多。」阿明（化名）口中的「出面」，是指「瞓街」，可以是連接尖沙嘴文化中心的行人隧道，也可以是深水埗通州街公園，或是福華街通宵營業的麥當勞，「行過仲見到好多人喺度，如果有改善，應該嗰個族群越來越少」。他曾是那族群的一員，夜宿快餐店的麥難民。<br />\n阿明在東莞工作10多年，大約3年前任職的工廠結業，不得已回流香港，卻沒地方住，惟有做麥難民。後來經社工轉介，他住過幾間政府資助的露宿者宿位，但限時進出，僅可住半年。1年多前，他改住社區組織協會「友家宿舍」，24小時開放方便他找到一份運輸工作，年已半百，暫算安穩，「過返正常生活」。<br />\n有瓦遮頭沒人想「瞓街」，但阿明發現街上的無家者，比起他3年前初次露宿街頭時增加很多，「我覺得香港係冇進步，停留咗喺度，因為冇改善到」。"},{"pid":"c5bc899884133e8910920a10c13fef73eb2813f7","tid":2447130,"uid":36494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T03:51:35.000Z","msg":"「香港差好遠！」前年隨社協到台北交流的穩叔說，當地政府會派發防水的儲物袋，讓無家者存放家當並安置在艋舺公園指定地方，有保安員看守。反觀香港，各部門用盡手段趕絕無家者，把家當作垃圾，公園每天洗地4次；近年社署資助的短期宿位更是零增長，無法應付不斷累增的無家者人口。"},{"pid":"506f59fa45ea4df1dc6dfdab2f765f9f18e2cc43","tid":2447130,"uid":3241,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T03:52:12.000Z","msg":"呢班人MPF 戶口隨時都有返10萬以上，但唔拎得黎用"},{"pid":"acf3d594174b5b1fe1a84b89fdef327aff6a75e3","tid":2447130,"uid":36494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T03:53:45.000Z","msg":"我自己都見越來越多露宿者"},{"pid":"bb2a9811836710a46a646e3740f7113f42345e9e","tid":2447130,"uid":367147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T03:56:23.000Z","msg":"登記左有咩著數<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8081eee5f62ce9655f0596d3aaa632a2fe9f8fa","tid":2447130,"uid":393145,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T03:57:07.000Z","msg":"社署指派飯增露宿者　<br />\n明哥：只想佢哋有兩餐溫飽<br />\n-<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n政府眼中<br />\n一定係太多人派飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n至有咁多人露宿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ab45492a4b5cbdff09e7df1c79cc84bb34ee9dd","tid":2447130,"uid":181819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T04:05:31.000Z","msg":"有150000先同我講"},{"pid":"3ccd56b4945f0466a9e0c52bb1a4037c122a3645","tid":2447130,"uid":50737,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T04:06:45.000Z","msg":"當年登記系統有問題，無登記應該有100000個，所以而家人數係少左，社會問題解決"},{"pid":"128854cc01a3257cda4264438976fe94b14fda3b","tid":2447130,"uid":273218,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T04:20:12.000Z","msg":"<del>回歸</del> <br />\n淪陷/97後/政權移交"},{"pid":"6d1e2eecc654e5805029ad18df30b5b2a9ea5a07","tid":2447130,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"506f59fa45ea4df1dc6dfdab2f765f9f18e2cc43","tid":2447130,"uid":3241,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T03:52:12.000Z","msg":"呢班人MPF 戶口隨時都有返10萬以上，但唔拎得黎用"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T07:05:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15bbb7bbc52c4e0ee477ecdd09b95e275ed0de53","tid":2447130,"uid":321374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T07:23:54.000Z","msg":"但支那人一落黎就有公屋<br />\n點解訓街果個唔係佢地？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}